{"tid":1536460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(70週年國慶活動) 全城黑衣至國慶","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T17:25:26.000Z","uid":282615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e95b7d4d9e199d88724172c47dbac2cb0bc8b955","tid":1536460,"uid":282615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"為使大眾一改黑衣觀念<br />\n誠邀大家參與<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>日日著黑衣</ins></span><br />\n除制服外，外出既衣物服飾以黑色為主調，直到國慶當日。<br />\n黑色，予人沉穩與莊重之感，西方隆重場合，均著上黑衣，我地就將此概念發揚光大吧！"},{"pid":"5f9b9cc08478fa738e0bfb93ff6d1b926e53b179","tid":1536460,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Gnbgry.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Gnbgry.jpg&h=076a76d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"dd50b47c094a574f3b502a1c3b3205f56e0cc0a7","tid":1536460,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-l